# Read Job Logs

## When to use

User asks for logs, output, or what happened with a job.

## Step 1: Get allocations

GET http://{{ nomad_server_ip }}:4646/v1/job/{job_id}/allocations

Use the first allocation's ID.

## Step 2: Read logs

GET http://{{ nomad_server_ip }}:4646/v1/client/fs/logs/{alloc_id}?task=execute&type=stdout&plain=true&origin=end&offset=16384

## Presentation

Summarize the key output. If logs are long, focus on results and errors. Don't dump raw text.
